QuestData.Title: Full Might of the Elves
QuestData.Description: Thalyssra managed to get all 3 to agree to the same thing? I am impressed with her skills of negotiation.$b$bAlright hero, Liadrin is already marching on Suramar. Join her forces.$b$bTyrande will flank the city defenders and meet you deeper in.$b$bThe Nightborne will bring up the rear and hold the territory for us.$b$bOculeth and I will move the Kirin Tor forces to Astravar Harbor. With luck, we shall see you on the other side.
QuestData.LogDescription: Lead the elven army to Astravar Harbor.
QuestData.RewardText: The telemancy traps you placed prior to the battle are doing wonders for reducing our losses.
